@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rcxkkt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.31 / tmp + 0.76)) - wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.98)))
    v0 = (v2 - v2)
    tmp = v1
    tmp = (0.42 * v0)
    v0 = (wp.abs(0.71) * (wp.sin(v2 + 1.00) - v1))
    v0 = ((0.93 + (tmp + 0.84 + tmp + 0.42)) * 0.61)
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
